courses.description: Use of database management software to create and maintain databases.

Training in keying business letters, multiple-page reports, tables, and special business forms. Attention to building speed with control. Student must type a minimum of 45 wpm with no more than 5 errors to pass this course. (PR: AAT 113)
Provides basic hands-on training in the use of word processing software. (PR: AAT 113 or permission)
